description_blz.en_US: Send a flickering flame towards your target, dealing 12,733 Fire damage to an enemy or healing an ally for 20,020.

description_blz.zh_TW: 朝目標發射閃曳烈焰，對一名敵人造成12,655點火焰傷害或使一名盟友恢復19,892點生命力。
